title: Do You Have Any Fake Friends?
itunes:title: Do You Have Any Fake Friends?
description:
Sometimes "fake" relationships can be more stressful than toxic ones. In this episode, I am going to teach you how to identify these relationships and what to do with these people so that you can maintain your sanity.
